results.name: Expansion of Product_{m>=1} (1+m*q^m)^-24.
comment: This sequence is obtained from the generalized Euler transform in A266964 by taking f(n) = 24, g(n) = -n. - _Seiichi Manyama_, Dec 30 2017
link: Seiichi Manyama, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000
